  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;Insufficient information has been provided to demonstrate that the neighbouring residents at No.49 Cranwich Road would not experience an undue loss of light as a result of the development. As such the development is contrary to LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-55cdc758-7fff-22a7-8bf0-3b76b0256d28&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The proposed rear extension by virtue of it&#x27;s depth and height along the boundary with No.49 would result in an increased sense of enclosure for the occupiers of No.49 and harm the outlook enjoyed by these residents to the detriment of their amenity. As such the development would be contrary to policy  LP2 (Development and Amenity) of Hackney Local Plan (2020). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
